name: Advanced photo
tagline: Advanced Photo does not require a long time to load, since it offers exclusively an image viewing function. The software allows you to open a wide variety of image formats, including some of the popular types, such as JPEG, BMP, GIF, and PNG.
body:
# Advanced_Photo
Advanced Photo does not require a long time to load, since it offers exclusively an image viewing function. The software allows you to open a wide variety of image formats, including some of the popular types, such as JPEG, BMP, GIF, and PNG.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
